          "message": {
            "text": "A script in TikTok's MAIN world can reproduce the public Companion bridge marker and forward oversized nested objects into extension runtime messaging and per-tab session state. Collection counts are bounded, but item and aggregate byte sizes are not, so the path can spoof local Companion state or exhaust extension-specific storage and processing resources."
          },
